 Miltrion warship IRONFIST

  
  "Alert. Temproal anomolie dectected."

  Panzertron walked over to the warship's sensor
computer.

  "Sensors indicate massive energy readings on the
planet surface," the drone reported," readings match
that of temporal proportions."

 "Hmm," Panzertron frowned,"Contact the Alliance and
inform them of what we have found. Is our project
nearly complete?"

  "Yes sir," another drone reported.

 "Excellent, find Zardus and tell him that as soon as
he can to come here, I want to show this to him personally."
